en_600502_0	Directorate of Psychological Operations at the Army Headquarters, adding a new facet to its training modules launched a programme, themed ‘Let's Visualize Her Through the Song’ on Wednesday (15) at the Sri Lanka Light Infantry Regiment Centre in collaboration with the Ministry of Women's and Children's Affairs.
en_600502_1	A total of 271 Army personnel, including Officers listened to the lectures and learnt more about how a woman in the pursuit of happiness tackles with challenges of life from birth to death.
en_600502_2	Several resource personnel, Mrs K. G. G Roshshini De Silva and Mr R. M. A Nimalsiri from the Ministry of Women's and Children's Affairs provided lectures to this awareness program with the help of the Sri Lanka Light Infantry Music Band which used vocals and instrumental music for this purpose.
